套問題 2020年有個商場解決 交通問題 依家已經起緊藍田隧道會駁埋入康城<br />\n環境問題 本身收緊廚餘 所以真係有臭味 但依家已經轉左收建築廢料 臭味問題已經解決 同埋個堆填區就爆 隨時過幾年會關閉埋 所以依家買定等升其實諗得過 <span style=\"color: red;\">但真係要守幾年</span></blockquote><br />\n第一期入伙果陣講到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSame <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  就算等到有埋商場 都唔會夠將軍澳市中心咁多野 偏埋左一邊"},{"pid":"ebb7a76a2ad4cdc6bebbad38c8d36970a29d7004","tid":390301,"uid":50101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T17:27:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>老實講 依家康城底水其實買得過 配套問題 2020年有個商場解決 交通問題 依家已經起緊藍田隧道會駁埋入康城<br />\n環境問題 本身收緊廚餘 所以真係有臭味 但依家已經轉左收建築廢料 臭味問題已經解決 同埋個堆填區就爆 隨時過幾年會關閉埋 所以依家買定等升其實諗得過 <span style=\"color: red;\">但真係要守幾年</span></blockquote><br />\n第一期入伙果陣講到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果時我買首都，周圍仲係地盤咩都冇<br />\n不過勝在樓價平，後尾唔住租比人買天晉真係無得比 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好歹都係地鐵上蓋，仲有兩房價錢可以住三房，當時嚟講係幾吸引"},{"pid":"f8f8fc208b38ee53894e1a526089572491b053cd","tid":390301,"uid":134880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:52:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係真的話  應該365日 都長長人龍</blockquote><br />\n得大家樂一間公眾餐廳"},{"pid":"f9fc7d7ff2df0f34d2e1336d0b2fee49bde30963","tid":390301,"uid":7824,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:56:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>住得康城家境斷估唔會差得去邊掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 揸車出入乜都搞掂啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 康城樓價平撚過啲居屋</blockquote><br />\nOn9 我住公屋都有部benz啦"},{"pid":"a2f73db6e2cf514b8c843dabdbbc1ea546574e02","tid":390301,"uid":26200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:00:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實當初點解會起地鐵</blockquote><br />\n發展商:港鐵公司"},{"pid":"8d5efb429197cf4d4ff9e3ac903cbe0fae771906","tid":390301,"uid":63394,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:39:06.000Z","msg":"屌你<br />\n我住左冇耐就開始研究廚藝"},{"pid":"1c20b4c11b2560af7e309664d2a1f686b36970d6","tid":390301,"uid":63394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:41:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最大問題我覺得係陣味</blockquote><br />\n其實無咩味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實堆填區轉左家居廢物好耐<br />\n咩味都冇<br />\n不過多蚊係真"},{"pid":"a327feb45eac8ec00f167e29a4259e006bb6a7f5","tid":390301,"uid":8572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:51:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>過多幾年唔同講法<br />\nD樓連商場一直起馬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n康城第一期2009年入伙，已經8年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陰公，唔計會所，舊年先有第一間食肆<br />\n買野仲係得一間惠康</blockquote><br />\n以前大家樂個位 都係惠康黎"},{"pid":"83ca0d67bf0e5716d7a7b1dcd41440ff61ca6c2d","tid":390301,"uid":132896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:53:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即管睇下康城發展完, 條藍田隧道起好未<br />\n而家基本上得一條將軍澳隧道入出將軍澳, 朝朝返工塞車慘過食屎</blockquote><br />\n真係仆街 <br />\n行山路都唔掂<br />\n山上又多左新屋村"},{"pid":"12aafc20f4e5310622577ee4cf5a5969328ac27e","tid":390301,"uid":35507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T12:51:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你<br />\n我住左冇耐就開始研究廚藝</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41d2058aeaf0b4b91ba04b41561470c4c359a8e","tid":390301,"uid":18065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T13:33:38.000Z","msg":"印象最深刻係落完雨啲黑色蟲飛哂出黎....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\"